---
layout : base.njk
title : Support Us
---

<main id="main" class="bg-gray-100 overflow-hidden">

	{% banner title %}

	<div class="container my-6">
		<h2 class="text-center separator-center">What We Do</h2>

		<div class="bg-secondary p-4 mb-6">
				<div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4 justify-center md:justify-between">
						<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4 text-center">
								<p class="text-6xl font-bold text-primary">40</p>
								<p class="h4 text-white">years in business</p>
						</div>

						<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4 text-center">
								<p class="text-6xl font-bold text-primary">2,000+</p>
								<p class="h4 text-white">service the community annually</p>
						</div>

						<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4 text-center">
								<p class="text-6xl font-bold text-primary">700</p>
								<p class="h4 text-white">competitive team members</p>
						</div>

						<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4 text-center">
								<p class="text-6xl font-bold text-primary">32</p>
								<p class="h4 text-white">USA Swimming Scholastic All-Americans in 2016–17</p>
						</div>
						<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4 text-center">
								<p class="text-6xl font-bold text-primary">30+</p>
								<p class="h4 text-white">LSC State Championships</p>
						</div>
						<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4 text-center">
								<p class="text-6xl font-bold text-primary">6</p>
								<p class="h4 text-white">National Titles</p>
						</div>
				</div>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
				<div class="p-6">
						<h2>Benefits of Becoming a Sponsor</h2>

						<div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4">
									<img class="mx-auto" src="/static/engage.png" alt="line drawing of hands with water drops falling onto them" width="80" height="80">
									<h3 class="text-center">Engage</h3>
									<p>Your support helps us engage in community involvement. Help the local community and charities.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4">
									<img class="mx-auto" src="/static/build.png" alt="line drawing of a person in water with a rainbow above them" width="74" height="80">
									<h3 class="text-center">Build</h3>
									<p>Your support helps us build strong kids, families, and communities as one of Charlotte’s best reputation as a competitive force in the sport of swimming.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4">
									<img class="mx-auto" src="/static/inspire.png" alt="line drawing of a swimmerwimmer" width="122" height="80">
									<h3 class="text-center">Inspire</h3>
									<p>Your support helps us Inspire young children from learn to swim to high level competitive swimmer with opportunities for college and great relationships and life skills.</p>
								</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4 text-center">
										<a class="button" href="/sponsors">Read More About Our Sponsors</a>
								</div>
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4 text-center">
										<a class="button" href="mailto:mcfee@swimmaccarolina.org?Subject=Hello%20Im%20interested%20in%20becoming%20a%20sponsor">I’m Interested in Becoming a Sponsor</a>
								</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4">
									<img class="p-4 shadow-md mx-auto" src="/static/care-300x200.jpg" alt="Coach talking to young swimmer" width="300" height="200">
								</div>
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4">
									<img class="p-4 shadow-md mx-auto" src="/static/swimSchool-300x200.jpg" alt="group of kids in the pool" width="300" height="200">
								</div>
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-4">
									<img class="p-4 shadow-md mx-auto" src="/static/mastersCap-300x200.jpg" alt="Adult female swimmers with Masters swim caps on" width="300" height="200">
								</div>
						</div>

						<h2>Donate</h2>
						<p>Your donation is important because it ensures the continuation of our classes, events, and outreach work through community support.</p>

						<div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4">
										<h3>Online</h3>
										<p>To donate electronically with a credit card or PayPal, click the Donate button to begin the process:</p>
										<p class="text-center">
												<a class="button" href="https://www.paypal.me/Swimmac" target="_blank" rel="external noopener">Donate</a>
										</p>
								</div>
								<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4">
										<h3>By Mail</h3>
										<p>You can mail your donation to:</p>
										<p class="street">9850 Providence Rd.,<br>
												Charlotte, NC 28277</p>
								</div>
						</div>

				</div>
		</div>
	</div>

</main>